                <div class="mt-6">
                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Strategic-Turnaround-Story-Government-Agency/dp/9785800881" target="_blank" class="bg-brandred text-sm text-white font-semibold leading-6 px-3 py-2 md:px-5 md:py-2 mr-2 my-4 rounded uppercase hover:bg-transparent hover:text-brandred hover:ring-brandred hover:ring-1 hover:transition">Buy on Amazon <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
